{"tid":1702940,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對上次喊到仆街已經係梁凌杰果次","createTime":"2019-11-10T04:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T08:59:57.000Z","uid":79793,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c05425eaa62f77277658e8253431d00feaaed423","tid":1702940,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以下全部內容純屬虛構,並不支持任何違法行為</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>琴日去果個集會,聽住首歌喊撚到仆街</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>諗番起</strong><br />\n<br />\n由第一次參加反送中遊行200萬人開始<br />\n因為貪玩,以為催淚彈冇料到企係最前線,粒催淚彈係我半米前面爆開,比三個FA救番<br />\n光復元朗元朗成條河兩邊鐵欄戰鼓聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n金鐘TG放題跑番去銅鑼灣,一粒粒催淚彈落係我腳邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次SET RB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次彌敦道賽跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次比狗車追,幾百個手足一齊跑入後街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次拎起舊磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次還擊追番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次自己區開花(你老母冇人)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每次都搞到凌晨,身心都開始頂唔撚緊<br />\n皮膚又敏感,又成撚日嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次凌晨好多人叫我快d走,但係後生過我嘅仲係到,我走左邊個睇住佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我雖然打唔贏狗,但係可以幫你擋子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好想有人可以同我一齊出去</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我諗頂多幾個月就唔撚得要走先</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講完,繼續番工,星期一三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c179bca5fc9fcdaed50609683c26cff7b82d73","tid":1702940,"uid":134975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:23:13.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"9a2f04ef191b704f7d47de76d6513858b3cee3ff","tid":1702940,"uid":306172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:23:43.000Z","msg":"共勉之"},{"pid":"cdb2fbe9b93cae796271e48e35fdbeb370af7afa","tid":1702940,"uid":322548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d863d3ecb4e3ac0c8b12a4a418b24307b07b1363","tid":1702940,"uid":322388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"雙十一 周圍塞"},{"pid":"04342a5cdbf59b1ff69dfe6f906c8567a608cd06","tid":1702940,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"［預言］涉強姦警員會孭起整隊警隊罪行，並可能全家被滅口<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1701986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1701986</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b50b97b05a5287a236aff81d82ce7e47ec96f2f0","tid":1702940,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:25:55.000Z","msg":"多謝寶馬媽媽,電單車叔叔,會計哥哥,仲有好多個車我番屋企嘅家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f2e792639f9bc2c335f87e4d415f39d650236b","tid":1702940,"uid":119585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB